                                    <h1>Odoo ERP Strategic Review &amp; Recommendations</h1>
                                    <div class="subtitle"><strong>Submitted to:</strong> Board of Directors - Al-Tahtheeb Schools</div>
                                    <div class="author">Prepared by: Nabil Al-Jallasi โ Project Consultant</div>
                                    <div class="subtitle">January 2026</div>
